body: Automated style fixes for #94, created by [Restyled][]. The following restylers [made fixes](https://restyled.io/gh/TokTok/repos/toktok-stack/jobs/265824): - astyle - autopep8 - black - clang-format - isort - reorder-python-imports - yapf To incorporate these changes, merge this Pull Request into the original. We recommend using the Squash or Rebase strategies. **NOTE**: As work continues on the original Pull Request, this process will re-run and update (force-push) this Pull Request with updated style fixes as necessary. If the style is fixed manually at any point (i.e. this process finds no fixes to make), this Pull Request will be closed automatically. Sorry if this was unexpected. To disable it, see our [documentation][].
